com.opengamma.strata.engine.config

Class DefaultMarketDataRules

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.engine.config.DefaultMarketDataRules
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarketDataRules, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class DefaultMarketDataRules
extends Object
implements MarketDataRules, ImmutableBean
    The default implementation of MarketDataRules containing a list of MarketDataRule instances.

    The rules are checked in order and the first matching rule is used.
